===========================================================================

CSE (on godwit): run:
cd && nohup syncthing &

To kill, first do:
killall syncthing

On WSL, once the syncthing binary was renamed to syncthing.old, and the
(new) syncthing binary was an empty file.

===========================================================================

To set up a new computer:
"Add remote device"
Computer IDs:
